## Quick Start

```bash
# Start the development server
docker compose up --build

# The API is available at http://localhost:8001/api/v1
# Admin panel at http://localhost:8001/admin/
```

## Commands

All commands run inside the Docker container:

```bash
docker compose exec app python manage.py startapp <name>       # Scaffold a new app
docker compose exec app python manage.py makemigrations [msg]  # Generate a migration
docker compose exec app python manage.py migrate               # Apply migrations
docker compose exec app python manage.py shell                 # IPython shell
docker compose exec app python manage.py createsuperuser       # Create an admin user
docker compose exec app pytest -v                              # Run tests
```

## Project Structure

```text
app/
├── djast/              # Core framework (settings, urls, db, commands)
├── admin/              # Built-in admin panel
├── auth/               # Built-in auth module
├── templates/          # Email templates
├── main.py             # ASGI entry point
├── manage.py           # CLI
└── requirements.txt    # Dependencies
```

